---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseHead 
title="Shipping Policy | Petstellation"
description="Shipping Policy for Petstellation digital products. Instant digital delivery information."
/>

<Header />

<main class="legal-page">

<h1>Shipping Policy</h1>

<p>Last updated: April 2026</p>

<h2>Digital Products Only</h2>

<p>
All products sold on Petstellation are digital downloads. 
No physical items will be shipped or delivered.
</p>

<h2>Instant Delivery</h2>

<p>
After a successful purchase, your digital files will be available for immediate download.
In most cases, you will also receive an email containing your download link.
</p>

<h2>Payment & Delivery Platform</h2>

<p>
All payments and digital product delivery are securely processed through 
:contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}.
</p>

<p>
Once your payment is confirmed, access to your files is granted automatically.
</p>

<h2>Delivery Issues</h2>

<p>
If you do not receive your download email within a few minutes, please check:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Your spam or junk folder</li>
<li>The email address used at checkout</li>
<li>Your payment confirmation status</li>
</ul>

<p>
If you still cannot access your files, please contact us and we will assist you promptly.
</p>

<h2>Incorrect Email Address</h2>

<p>
If an incorrect email address was entered at checkout, please contact support with your order details
so we can help resolve the issue.
</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>

<p>
If you have any questions regarding delivery, please visit our Contact Information page.
</p>

</main>

<Footer />
